title.narrative: Caring for Children and Empowering Young People (C2EYP)

description.narrative: The Caring for Children and Empowering Young People project, a 5-year, USAID-funded award. The goal of the project is to enable more Tanzanian OVC (children, adolescents, and young people orphaned and made vulnerable by HIV and other adversities) to utilize age-appropriate HIV/AIDS-related and other services for improved care, health, nutrition, education, protection, livelihoods, and psychosocial well-being.
